title: Kid 90 with Soleil Moon Frye!
description:
Soleil Moon Frye (Punky Brewster) joins Tig and Cheryl to talk about her new autobiographical Hulu doc "Kid 90." Soleil shares some crazy stories about Charlie Sheen, Michael Jackson, and even Bubbles the chimpanzee. It's an incredible and candid discussion, full of hilarious tangents and bean spillage as always! *this episode contains spoilers* (tigandcheryltruestory@gmail.com)
